data.description:
Charming 3 Bed, 2 Bath Home on North Beach St., Ormond Beach - Steps from the Intra Coastal Waterway. Embrace the coastal lifestyle in this meticulously maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bath residence, ideally located on North Beach St. in the heart of Ormond Beach. Situated just across from the Intra Coastal Waterway and amidst multi-million dollar estates, this home offers both tranquility and elegance in Ormond Beach.Step inside to discover the seamless blend of comfort and style, with numerous updates throughout enhancing the charm of this inviting home and enjoy evenings by the beautiful fireplace that adds character and warmth to the heart of the home. Retreat to the oversized screened back patio, a perfect sanctuary for relaxation and entertaining, surrounded by lush landscaping Experience the allure of waterfront living with the Intra Coastal Waterway just across the street, providing breathtaking views, gorgeous sunrises, and inspiring walks along the water's edge.
Revel in the beauty of an oversized lot meticulously landscaped with custom concrete curbing, creating an aesthetic harmony that complements the home and add in a versatile 8x14 workshop/shed catering to your DIY projects and storage needs. 
Enjoy the well-maintained above ground hot tub, offering a serene escape to unwind and soak in the pleasures of coastal living. A newer riding lawnmower comes included, ensuring ease in maintaining the sprawling yard, leaving you more time to enjoy the finer things.

Indulge in the ultimate blend of comfort, elegance, and coastal allure. This home presents a rare opportunity to live amidst the splendor of the Intra Coastal Waterway and neighboring luxury estates.
